<p data-start="451" data-end="543">⭐ <em data-start="453" data-end="473">Best simple title:</em> <strong data-start="474" data-end="543">MediRead – AI-Based Prescription Interpreter for Rural Healthcare</strong></p>
<hr data-start="545" data-end="548">
<h2 data-section-id="1ehl6qz" data-start="550" data-end="570">Problem Statement</h2>
<p data-start="571" data-end="879">In many rural areas, patients often struggle to understand doctors' handwritten prescriptions due to poor handwriting, medical terminology, and lack of medical knowledge. This confusion can lead to incorrect medication usage, missed doses, or improper treatment, which may negatively affect patient health.</p>
<p data-start="881" data-end="1210">There is a need for an intelligent system that can read and interpret handwritten prescriptions, convert them into clear and understandable text, and provide simple instructions on how and when to take medicines. The system should also send reminders or notifications to help patients take their medication at the correct time.</p>
<p data-start="1212" data-end="1456">This project aims to develop an <strong data-start="1244" data-end="1283">AI-powered prescription interpreter</strong> that extracts information from handwritten prescriptions, translates it into simple language, and assists rural patients in following their medication schedules accurately.</p>
<hr data-start="1458" data-end="1461">
