<hr data-start="216" data-end="219">
<h1 data-section-id="6f39i0" data-start="221" data-end="270">✅ Final Tech Stack (Optimized for Your Project)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1i26ny6" data-start="272" data-end="291">🧠 AI / ML Layer</h2>
<ul data-start="292" data-end="644">
<li data-section-id="1akjtzf" data-start="292" data-end="413">
<p data-start="294" data-end="310"><strong data-start="294" data-end="308">OCR Model:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="313" data-end="413">
<li data-section-id="15i97xt" data-start="313" data-end="342">
<p data-start="315" data-end="342">EasyOCR <em data-start="323" data-end="340">(fast &amp; simple)</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8ywoex" data-start="345" data-end="413">
<p data-start="347" data-end="413">OR <strong data-start="350" data-end="384">TrOCR (Microsoft, HuggingFace)</strong> <em data-start="385" data-end="411">(better for handwriting)</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14xqkvy" data-start="415" data-end="644">
<p data-start="417" data-end="453"><strong data-start="417" data-end="451">Text Cleaning &amp; Understanding:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="456" data-end="644">
<li data-section-id="6m9cq1" data-start="456" data-end="494">
<p data-start="458" data-end="494"><strong data-start="458" data-end="492">LLM (OpenAI / Llama / Mistral)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p4g3un" data-start="497" data-end="644">
<p data-start="499" data-end="548">Use <strong data-start="503" data-end="543">RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)</strong> for:</p>
<ul data-start="553" data-end="644">
<li data-section-id="1mgfbr1" data-start="553" data-end="581">
<p data-start="555" data-end="581">Medicine name correction</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s753xc" data-start="586" data-end="608">
<p data-start="588" data-end="608">Dosage explanation</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vlh0rj" data-start="613" data-end="644">
<p data-start="615" data-end="644">Simple language translation</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="646" data-end="657">👉 Replace:</p>
<ul data-start="658" data-end="744">
<li data-section-id="14s0vr7" data-start="658" data-end="693">
<p data-start="660" data-end="693">❌ Whisper (speech → not needed)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="174ry2c" data-start="694" data-end="744">
<p data-start="696" data-end="744">❌ BART/PEGASUS (summarization → not core here)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="746" data-end="749">
<h2 data-section-id="1a50g6v" data-start="751" data-end="764">⚙️ Backend</h2>
<ul data-start="765" data-end="989">
<li data-section-id="185qlc2" data-start="765" data-end="805">
<p data-start="767" data-end="805"><strong data-start="767" data-end="781">Framework:</strong> FastAPI (recommended)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1alsx3o" data-start="806" data-end="830">
<p data-start="808" data-end="830"><strong data-start="808" data-end="821">Language:</strong> Python</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y8w6a" data-start="831" data-end="989">
<p data-start="833" data-end="847"><strong data-start="833" data-end="847">Libraries:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="850" data-end="989">
<li data-section-id="38835c" data-start="850" data-end="882">
<p data-start="852" data-end="882">OpenCV → image preprocessing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10sn6pf" data-start="885" data-end="912">
<p data-start="887" data-end="912">Pillow → image handling</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ewykcn" data-start="915" data-end="947">
<p data-start="917" data-end="947">Torch / Transformers → TrOCR</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mpo4j1" data-start="950" data-end="989">
<p data-start="952" data-end="989">EasyOCR (if using lightweight option)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="991" data-end="994">
