<hr data-start="100" data-end="103">
<h1 data-section-id="14vfv9l" data-start="105" data-end="179">✅ Proposed Model: AI-Based Prescription Interpretation System (RxAssist)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="l63aon" data-start="181" data-end="195">📌 Overview</h2>
<p data-start="196" data-end="486">The proposed system is an <strong data-start="222" data-end="272">AI-powered prescription understanding platform</strong> designed to help rural users interpret handwritten doctor prescriptions. It converts unclear handwritten text into readable content and provides simple, actionable instructions along with reminders for medication.</p>
<hr data-start="488" data-end="491">
<h2 data-section-id="w25omf" data-start="493" data-end="527">⚙️ Working Model (Step-by-Step)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1tque3s" data-start="529" data-end="557">🖼️ 1. Input Acquisition</h3>
