<hr data-start="62" data-end="65">
<p data-start="67" data-end="224">The system follows a <strong data-start="88" data-end="120">modular layered architecture</strong>, integrating OCR, NLP, and notification services into an AI-powered prescription assistance platform.</p>
<ul data-start="226" data-end="1146">
<li data-section-id="11o7jgh" data-start="226" data-end="315">
<p data-start="228" data-end="315">The <strong data-start="232" data-end="260">Image Acquisition Module</strong> captures or uploads handwritten prescription images.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kwkj3x" data-start="317" data-end="433">
<p data-start="319" data-end="433">The <strong data-start="323" data-end="347">Preprocessing Module</strong> enhances image quality using grayscale conversion, noise removal, and thresholding.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1508k8v" data-start="435" data-end="519">
<p data-start="437" data-end="519">The <strong data-start="441" data-end="455">OCR Module</strong> (TrOCR/EasyOCR) extracts text from handwritten prescriptions.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i4suqd" data-start="521" data-end="632">
<p data-start="523" data-end="632">The <strong data-start="527" data-end="559">Text Processing &amp; NLP Module</strong> cleans and structures text, identifying medicines and dosage patterns.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="g7uj96" data-start="634" data-end="743">
<p data-start="636" data-end="743">The <strong data-start="640" data-end="680">AI Interpretation Module (LLM + RAG)</strong> simplifies medical instructions into user-friendly language.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1q6n6hm" data-start="745" data-end="841">
<p data-start="747" data-end="841">The <strong data-start="751" data-end="774">Core Service Module</strong> generates readable prescription output and medication schedules.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xgb3ew" data-start="843" data-end="919">
<p data-start="845" data-end="919">The <strong data-start="849" data-end="872">Notification Module</strong> sends reminders via SMS, Gmail, or Calendar.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11lre6f" data-start="921" data-end="1006">
<p data-start="923" data-end="1006">The <strong data-start="927" data-end="959">Database Module (PostgreSQL)</strong> stores prescriptions and schedules securely.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nr97sc" data-start="1008" data-end="1068">
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1068">The <strong data-start="1014" data-end="1036">API Security Layer</strong> ensures secure communication.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sdmjoh" data-start="1070" data-end="1146">
<p data-start="1072" data-end="1146">The <strong data-start="1076" data-end="1108">Authentication &amp; RBAC Module</strong> manages access based on user roles.</p>
</li>
</ul>
