<hr data-start="157" data-end="160">
<h2 data-section-id="1d3os9u" data-start="162" data-end="203">✅ Literature-Based Model Justification</h2>
<p data-start="205" data-end="340">The proposed system is supported by existing research in <strong data-start="262" data-end="339">handwritten prescription recognition and AI-based medical text processing</strong>.</p>
<ul data-start="342" data-end="1409">
<li data-section-id="1mv6sr0" data-start="342" data-end="556">
<p data-start="344" data-end="556">Studies show that <strong data-start="362" data-end="418">handwritten prescriptions are difficult to interpret</strong> due to variability in writing styles and formats, making automated extraction a challenging task. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uok65q" data-start="558" data-end="785">
<p data-start="560" data-end="785">Recent approaches use <strong data-start="582" data-end="645">deep learning and Transformer-based OCR models (like TrOCR)</strong> to accurately extract text from prescriptions, achieving very low error rates and high reliability. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ybgmum" data-start="787" data-end="986">
<p data-start="789" data-end="986">Research also highlights that combining <strong data-start="829" data-end="860">image segmentation with OCR</strong> improves accuracy by focusing on relevant regions such as medicine names and dosages. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15wza43" data-start="988" data-end="1196">
<p data-start="990" data-end="1196">Large-scale studies on medical records indicate that <strong data-start="1043" data-end="1114">AI models can successfully extract medicines and dosage information</strong>, even from complex handwritten documents. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.09729?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.09729?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bm1qnm" data-start="1198" data-end="1409">
<p data-start="1200" data-end="1409">Literature reviews confirm that <strong data-start="1232" data-end="1271">OCR combined with AI/NLP techniques</strong> is an effective approach to convert handwritten documents into structured, readable digital data. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2001.00139?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2001.00139?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1411" data-end="1414">
<h2 data-section-id="300qx1" data-start="1416" data-end="1463">🎯 Conclusion (Add this line in your report)</h2>
<p data-start="1464" data-end="1637">👉 <em data-start="1467" data-end="1637">“Based on existing research, integrating OCR with AI and NLP techniques provides an effective and scalable solution for interpreting handwritten medical prescriptions.”</em></p>
