<hr data-start="121" data-end="124">
<h1 data-section-id="iubjcg" data-start="126" data-end="168">✅ Architecture Diagram – RxAssist System</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="170" data-end="2110"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>                ┌───────────────────────────────┐</span><br><span>                │        User Input Layer        │</span><br><span>                │  (Prescription Image Upload)   │</span><br><span>                └───────────────┬───────────────┘</span><br><span>                                │</span><br><span>                                ▼</span><br><span>                ┌───────────────────────────────┐</span><br><span>                │      API Gateway Layer         │</span><br><span>                │  (FastAPI / Request Handling)  │</span><br><span>                └───────────────┬───────────────┘</span><br><span>                                │</span><br><span>        ┌───────────────────────┼────────────────────────┐</span><br><span>        ▼                       ▼                        ▼</span><br><span>┌───────────────┐   ┌────────────────────┐   ┌────────────────────┐</span><br><span>│ Preprocessing │   │     OCR Module     │   │  Security Layer     │</span><br><span>│ (OpenCV)      │   │ (TrOCR/EasyOCR)    │   │ (Auth + Encryption) │</span><br><span>└──────┬────────┘   └──────────┬─────────┘   └────────────────────┘</span><br><span>       │                       │</span><br><span>       ▼                       ▼</span><br><span>                ┌───────────────────────────────┐</span><br><span>                │   Text Processing &amp; NLP Layer │</span><br><span>                │ (Cleaning + Entity Extraction)│</span><br><span>                └───────────────┬───────────────┘</span><br><span>                                │</span><br><span>                                ▼</span><br><span>                ┌───────────────────────────────┐</span><br><span>                │   AI Interpretation Layer      │</span><br><span>                │     (LLM + RAG System)         │</span><br><span>                └───────────────┬───────────────┘</span><br><span>                                │</span><br><span>        ┌───────────────────────┼────────────────────────┐</span><br><span>        ▼                       ▼                        ▼</span><br><span>┌────────────────┐   ┌────────────────────┐   ┌────────────────────┐</span><br><span>│ Core Service   │   │ Notification Layer │   │   Database Layer    │</span><br><span>│ (Output +      │   │ (SMS / Gmail /     │   │   (PostgreSQL)      │</span><br><span>│ Scheduling)    │   │  Calendar API)     │   │                    │</span><br><span>└────────────────┘   └────────────────────┘   └────────────────────┘</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2112" data-end="2115">
<h2 data-section-id="1u6m7bq" data-start="2117" data-end="2163">🎯 How to Explain (Very Important for Viva)</h2>
<p data-start="2165" data-end="2383">👉 “The system follows a layered architecture where the input image is processed through OCR and NLP layers, enhanced using LLM for understanding, and finally connected to services like reminders and database storage.”</p>
<hr data-start="2385" data-end="2388">
<h2 data-section-id="10onn8l" data-start="2390" data-end="2422">🔥 Pro Tips (to score higher)</h2>
<ul data-start="2423" data-end="2626">
<li data-section-id="1d6stbx" data-start="2423" data-end="2482">
<p data-start="2425" data-end="2482">Draw this in <strong data-start="2438" data-end="2482">draw.io / PowerPoint with boxes + arrows</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="160mmjd" data-start="2483" data-end="2626">
<p data-start="2485" data-end="2520">Use <strong data-start="2489" data-end="2519">different colors per layer</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="2523" data-end="2626">
<li data-section-id="rsqf0l" data-start="2523" data-end="2543">
<p data-start="2525" data-end="2543">Blue → Input/API</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oe874d" data-start="2546" data-end="2571">
<p data-start="2548" data-end="2571">Green → AI/Processing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="d310ro" data-start="2574" data-end="2595">
<p data-start="2576" data-end="2595">Orange → Services</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1331y3v" data-start="2598" data-end="2626">
<p data-start="2600" data-end="2626">Gray → Database/Security</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
