-end flow using ONLY APIs (no local models)</strong> to detect handwritten prescription text and return output. Here’s a clean, practical flow you can use 👇</p>
<hr data-start="187" data-end="190">
<h1 data-section-id="1tij1hp" data-start="192" data-end="238">✅ Complete Flow (API-Based – No Local Model)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="rbqfgr" data-start="240" data-end="257">🔄 System Flow</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="259" data-end="341"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>User → Upload Image → Backend API → Cloud OCR API → Text Cleaning → Output</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="343" data-end="346">
<h2 data-section-id="uxc1m" data-start="348" data-end="371">⚙️ Step-by-Step Flow</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="svovtz" data-start="373" data-end="414">📥 1. User Uploads Prescription Image</h3>
<ul data-start="415" data-end="492">
<li data-section-id="1n52g6c" data-start="415" data-end="456">
<p data-start="417" data-end="456">User sends image (JPG/PNG) to backend</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lsu1ro" data-start="457" data-end="492">
<p data-start="459" data-end="492">Via API request (<code data-start="476" data-end="491">POST /predict</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="494" data-end="497">
<h3 data-section-id="12xvv4y" data-start="499" data-end="543">🌐 2. Backend Receives Request (FastAPI)</h3>
<ul data-start="544" data-end="635">
<li data-section-id="18xlmtl" data-start="544" data-end="565">
<p data-start="546" data-end="565">Accept image file</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nqta2y" data-start="566" data-end="598">
<p data-start="568" data-end="598">Convert image to byte format</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1x7fyfa" data-start="599" data-end="635">
<p data-start="601" data-end="635">Prepare request for external API</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="637" data-end="640">
<h3 data-section-id="9pkdjz" data-start="642" data-end="680">🤖 3. Call OCR API (Using API Key)</h3>
<p data-start="681" data-end="698">Use any of these:</p>
<ul data-start="700" data-end="781">
<li data-section-id="1t7pqxo" data-start="700" data-end="730">
<p data-start="702" data-end="730"><strong data-start="702" data-end="730">Google Vision API (Best)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5ayxjo" data-start="731" data-end="749">
<p data-start="733" data-end="749"><strong data-start="733" data-end="749">AWS Textract</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uqo570" data-start="750" data-end="781">
<p data-start="752" data-end="781"><strong data-start="752" data-end="781">Azure Computer Vision OCR</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="783" data-end="810">👉 Example (Google Vision):</p>
<ul data-start="811" data-end="886">
<li data-section-id="86hvjb" data-start="811" data-end="840">
<p data-start="813" data-end="840">Send image (base64 encoded)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1t66z23" data-start="841" data-end="858">
<p data-start="843" data-end="858">Include API key</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="w6f5ri" data-start="859" data-end="886">
<p data-start="861" data-end="886">Request: <code data-start="870" data-end="886">TEXT_DETECTION</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="888" data-end="891">
<h3 data-section-id="c99tjb" data-start="893" data-end="923">📄 4. OCR API Returns Text</h3>
<ul data-start="924" data-end="960">
<li data-section-id="2louey" data-start="924" data-end="960">
<p data-start="926" data-end="960">API gives raw extracted text like:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="961" data-end="1007"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Tab Paracetamol 500mg</span><br><span>1-0-1 after food</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1009" data-end="1012">
<h3 data-section-id="1yzg59" data-start="1014" data-end="1058">🧹 5. Text Cleaning (Backend Logic Only)</h3>
<ul data-start="1059" data-end="1133">
<li data-section-id="16cu5cd" data-start="1059" data-end="1086">
<p data-start="1061" data-end="1086">Remove unwanted symbols</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="w71cfy" data-start="1087" data-end="1102">
<p data-start="1089" data-end="1102">Fix spacing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="j4w3pu" data-start="1103" data-end="1133">
<p data-start="1105" data-end="1133">Format into readable lines</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1135" data-end="1146">👉 Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1147" data-end="1215"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Paracetamol 500mg</span><br><span>Take 1 tablet morning and night after food</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1217" data-end="1220">
<h3 data-section-id="3ai55q" data-start="1222" data-end="1251">📤 6. Return Final Output</h3>
<ul data-start="1252" data-end="1324">
<li data-section-id="6b4d1l" data-start="1252" data-end="1288">
<p data-start="1254" data-end="1288">Send ONLY clean text as response</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="163x03v" data-start="1289" data-end="1324">
<p data-start="1291" data-end="1324">No JSON (as per your requirement)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1326" data-end="1329">
<h1 data-section-id="f9djxu" data-start="1331" data-end="1358">✅ Simple API Flow Diagram</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1360" data-end="1504"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>[User]</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>[FastAPI Backend]</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>[OCR API (Google Vision / AWS Textract)]</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>[Text Cleaning Logic]</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>[Final Readable Text Output]</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1506" data-end="1509">
<h1 data-section-id="1a1pnvv" data-start="1511" data-end="1549">✅ Example Code Flow (Very Important)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="t28i15" data-start="1551" data-end="1585">🔑 API Call Logic (Pseudo Code)</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1587" data-end="2156"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">requests</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">base64</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">extract_text</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">image_path</span><span>):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">with</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">open</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">image_path</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"rb"</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼn">as</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">img</span><span>:</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼt">encoded</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">base64</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>b64encode(</span><span class="ͼt">img</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>read())</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>decode()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">url</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"https://vision.googleapis.com/v1/images:annotate?key=YOUR_API_KEY"</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">body</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"requests"</span><span>: [</span><br><span>            {</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"image"</span><span>: {</span><span class="ͼr">"content"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">encoded</span><span>},</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"features"</span><span>: [{</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"TEXT_DETECTION"</span><span>}]</span><br><span>            }</span><br><span>        ]</span><br><span>    }</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">response</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">requests</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>post(</span><span class="ͼt">url</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">json</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">body</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">text</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">response</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>json()[</span><span class="ͼr">'responses'</span><span>][</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>][</span><span class="ͼr">'fullTextAnnotation'</span><span>][</span><span class="ͼr">'text'</span><span>]</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">text</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2158" data-end="2161">
<h1 data-section-id="1fbpfdm" data-start="2163" data-end="2193">🎯 Why This Approach is Good</h1>
