r="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="332b2bea-2264-42c6-946e-cb6178ad4f2c" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="177">Yes — <strong data-start="6" data-end="55">you absolutely <em data-start="23" data-end="28">can</em> (and should) use FastAPI</strong> 👍<br data-start="58" data-end="61">
FastAPI is just your <strong data-start="82" data-end="101">backend wrapper</strong>, while the OCR is done by external APIs like Google Vision or AWS Textract.</p>
<p data-start="179" data-end="206">Let me clarify it simply 👇</p>
<hr data-start="208" data-end="211">
<h1 data-section-id="1t69ymo" data-start="213" data-end="248">✅ How FastAPI Fits in Your System</h1>
<p data-start="250" data-end="335">👉 FastAPI is <strong data-start="264" data-end="285">NOT replacing OCR</strong><br data-start="285" data-end="288">
👉 It acts as the <strong data-start="306" data-end="335">middle layer (controller)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="337" data-end="340">
<h2 data-section-id="1wx11sn" data-start="342" data-end="368">🔄 Correct Architecture</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="370" data-end="440"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>User → FastAPI → OCR API (Google/AWS/Azure) → FastAPI → Output</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="442" data-end="445">
<h2 data-section-id="cxc87w" data-start="447" data-end="470">⚙️ What FastAPI Does</h2>
<ul data-start="471" data-end="609">
<li data-section-id="1da9eqj" data-start="471" data-end="498">
<p data-start="473" data-end="498">Accepts image from user</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="imtq32" data-start="499" data-end="536">
<p data-start="501" data-end="536">Sends it to OCR API using API key</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="uyp3gh" data-start="537" data-end="564">
<p data-start="539" data-end="564">Receives extracted text</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1q3fa56" data-start="565" data-end="584">
<p data-start="567" data-end="584">Cleans the text</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yzc2w2" data-start="585" data-end="609">
<p data-start="587" data-end="609">Returns final output</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="611" data-end="614">
<h2 data-section-id="1k3lydg" data-start="616" data-end="647">✅ Example Flow Using FastAPI</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1f6o68m" data-start="649" data-end="674">1. User sends request</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="675" data-end="709"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>POST /predict</span><br><span>(image file)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="711" data-end="714">
<h3 data-section-id="12j8ah2" data-start="716" data-end="741">2. FastAPI handles it</h3>
<ul data-start="742" data-end="780">
<li data-section-id="oo2oi6" data-start="742" data-end="757">
<p data-start="744" data-end="757">Reads image</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1krvw8w" data-start="758" data-end="780">
<p data-start="760" data-end="780">Converts to base64</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="782" data-end="785">
<h3 data-section-id="1mdswes" data-start="787" data-end="815">3. FastAPI calls OCR API</h3>
<ul data-start="816" data-end="865">
<li data-section-id="185klbq" data-start="816" data-end="848">
<p data-start="818" data-end="848">Google Vision / AWS Textract</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kb20k7" data-start="849" data-end="865">
<p data-start="851" data-end="865">Uses API key</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="867" data-end="870">
<h3 data-section-id="l1qpiy" data-start="872" data-end="905">4. FastAPI processes response</h3>
<ul data-start="906" data-end="935">
<li data-section-id="n0lkuw" data-start="906" data-end="922">
<p data-start="908" data-end="922">Extract text</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="u9hddc" data-start="923" data-end="935">
<p data-start="925" data-end="935">Clean it</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="937" data-end="940">
<h3 data-section-id="mrpcyr" data-start="942" data-end="971">5. FastAPI returns output</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="972" data-end="1042"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Paracetamol 500mg  </span><br><span>Take 1 tablet morning and night after food</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1044" data-end="1047">
<h1 data-section-id="3q9bp" data-start="1049" data-end="1092">✅ Simple Working Code (FastAPI + OCR API)</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1094" data-end="1898"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">fastapi</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">FastAPI</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">UploadFile</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">File</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">base64</span><br><span class="ͼn">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">requests</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">app</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">FastAPI</span><span>()</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">API_KEY</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"YOUR_GOOGLE_VISION_API_KEY"</span><br><br><span class="ͼm">@</span><span class="ͼt">app</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span class="ͼt">post</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"/predict"</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼn">async</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">predict</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">file</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">UploadFile</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">File</span><span>(...)):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">image_bytes</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">await</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">file</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>read()</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">encoded</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">base64</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>b64encode(</span><span class="ͼt">image_bytes</span><span>)</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>decode()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">url</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">f"https://vision.googleapis.com/v1/images:annotate?key=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼt">API_KEY</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼr">"</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">body</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> {</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼr">"requests"</span><span>: [</span><br><span>            {</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"image"</span><span>: {</span><span class="ͼr">"content"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼt">encoded</span><span>},</span><br><span>                </span><span class="ͼr">"features"</span><span>: [{</span><span class="ͼr">"type"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼr">"TEXT_DETECTION"</span><span>}]</span><br><span>            }</span><br><span>        ]</span><br><span>    }</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">response</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">requests</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>post(</span><span class="ͼt">url</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼt">json</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼt">body</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">result</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">response</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>json()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">text</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">result</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼr">'responses'</span><span>][</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>]</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">'fullTextAnnotation'</span><span>, {})</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>get(</span><span class="ͼr">'text'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">''</span><span>)</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼl"># simple cleaning</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼt">cleaned_text</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">text</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>strip()</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼn">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">cleaned_text</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1900" data-end="1903">
<h1 data-section-id="121ihap" data-start="1905" data-end="1936">🎯 Key Point (Very Important)</h1>
<p data-start="1938" data-end="2027">👉 FastAPI = <strong data-start="1951" data-end="1969">Backend server</strong><br data-start="1969" data-end="1972">
👉 OCR API = <strong data-start="1985" data-end="2025">Actual intelligence (text detection)</strong></p>
<p data-start="2029" data-end="2075">You are just <strong data-start="2042" data-end="2075">connecting them using API key</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2077" data-end="2080">
<h1 data-section-id="iidh8b" data-start="2082" data-end="2111">⚡ When to Use This Approach</h1>
<ul data-start="2112" data-end="2178">
<li data-section-id="1coltr7" data-start="2112" data-end="2128">
<p data-start="2114" data-end="2128">Hackathons ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6kbohy" data-start="2129" data-end="2150">
<p data-start="2131" data-end="2150">Quick prototype ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mtqndy" data-start="2151" data-end="2178">
<p data-start="2153" data-end="2178">No ML training needed ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2180" data-end="2183">
<h1 data-section-id="x7a0ku" data-start="2185" data-end="2204">❗ When NOT Enough</h1>
<p data-start="2205" data-end="2224">Later, if you want:</p>
<ul data-start="2225" data-end="2302">
<li data-section-id="1v5plxa" data-start="2225" data-end="2256">
<p data-start="2227" data-end="2256">Better handwriting accuracy</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wsm7jc" data-start="2257" data-end="2283">
<p data-start="2259" data-end="2283">Medicine understanding</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12769cc" data-start="2284" data-end="2302">
<p data-start="2286" data-end="2302">Offline system</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2304" data-end="2339">👉 Then you move to <strong data-start="2324" data-end="2339">TrOCR + LLM</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2341" data-end="2344">
<h2 data-section-id="cysruc" data-start="2346" data-end="2378">🔥 One-Line Answer (for viva)</h2>
<p data-start="2379" data-end="2510">👉 <em data-start="2382" data-end="2510">“Yes, FastAPI is used as the backend to handle requests and integrate with cloud OCR APIs using API keys for text extraction.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="2512" data-end="2515">
