Since you created a <strong data-start="80" data-end="99">Service Account</strong>, you actually <strong data-start="114" data-end="144">DON’T use a normal API key</strong>. Instead, you use a <strong data-start="165" data-end="190">JSON credentials file</strong>.</p>
