<hr data-start="220" data-end="223">
<h1 data-section-id="167giu6" data-start="225" data-end="262">✅ Two Ways to Use Google Vision API</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1louq6q" data-start="264" data-end="324">🟢 Option 1: API Key (Simple – Recommended for Hackathon)</h2>
<ul data-start="325" data-end="450">
<li data-section-id="1kf3dn9" data-start="325" data-end="390">
<p data-start="327" data-end="390">Go to: <strong data-start="334" data-end="390">Google Cloud Console → APIs &amp; Services → Credentials</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ybob9i" data-start="391" data-end="433">
<p data-start="393" data-end="433">Click <strong data-start="399" data-end="433">“Create Credentials” → API Key</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qv6ncz" data-start="434" data-end="450">
<p data-start="436" data-end="450">Copy the key</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="452" data-end="485">👉 Use this in your FastAPI code:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="486" data-end="559"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://vision.googleapis.com/v1/images:annotate?key=YOUR_API_KEY</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="561" data-end="564">
<h2 data-section-id="etahbd" data-start="566" data-end="638">🔵 Option 2: Service Account (More Secure – You Already Created This)</h2>
<p data-start="640" data-end="678">Since you already created it, do this:</p>
<hr data-start="680" data-end="683">
<h1 data-section-id="1jgx9sc" data-start="685" data-end="724">✅ How to Get API from Service Account</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="1ckkiv0" data-start="726" data-end="758">📥 Step 1: Download JSON Key</h3>
<ul data-start="759" data-end="940">
<li data-section-id="v71epc" data-start="759" data-end="802">
<p data-start="761" data-end="802">Go to: <strong data-start="768" data-end="802">IAM &amp; Admin → Service Accounts</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1r9x71n" data-start="803" data-end="833">
<p data-start="805" data-end="833">Click your service account</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1his7bc" data-start="834" data-end="854">
<p data-start="836" data-end="854">Go to <strong data-start="842" data-end="854">Keys tab</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5flm4n" data-start="855" data-end="898">
<p data-start="857" data-end="898">Click <strong data-start="863" data-end="898">Add Key → Create new key → JSON</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sjy3rx" data-start="899" data-end="940">
<p data-start="901" data-end="940">Download file (e.g., <code data-start="922" data-end="939">vision-key.json</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="942" data-end="945">
<h3 data-section-id="yfsml7" data-start="947" data-end="986">⚙️ Step 2: Set Environment Variable</h3>
<p data-start="988" data-end="1011">In your project folder:</p>
<h4 data-start="1013" data-end="1039">Windows (PowerShell):</h4>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1040" data-end="1116"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>setx GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS </span><span class="ͼr">"C:\path\to\vision-key.json"</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
