den="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="703c72c7-1c01-469b-9038-6733083e6392" data-testid="conversation-turn-32" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="703c72c7-1c01-469b-9038-6733083e6392" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="120">This depends on <strong data-start="16" data-end="57">which type of credentials you created</strong> — API Key vs Service Account. I’ll help you find it quickly 👇</p>
<hr data-start="122" data-end="125">
<h1 data-section-id="mhftd5" data-start="127" data-end="207"><span role="text">🔍 Case 1: If You Created an <strong data-start="158" data-end="169">API Key</strong> (what you need for your current code)</span></h1>
<h3 data-section-id="1a4zgaq" data-start="209" data-end="233">📍 Where to find it:</h3>
<ol data-start="234" data-end="375">
<li data-section-id="15yf2g6" data-start="234" data-end="267">
<p data-start="237" data-end="267">Go to <strong data-start="243" data-end="267">Google Cloud Console</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yfr7hk" data-start="268" data-end="325">
<p data-start="271" data-end="325">Navigate to:<br data-start="283" data-end="286">
👉 <strong data-start="292" data-end="325">APIs &amp; Services → Credentials</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="189l2ts" data-start="326" data-end="375">
<p data-start="329" data-end="375">Under <strong data-start="335" data-end="347">API Keys</strong>, you’ll see something like:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="377" data-end="403"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>AIzaSyXXXXXXX.....</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="405" data-end="443">👉 That <strong data-start="413" data-end="443">long string = your API key</strong></p>
<hr data-start="445" data-end="448">
<h3 data-section-id="1ren59p" data-start="450" data-end="469">✅ What to copy:</h3>
<p data-start="470" data-end="504">👉 Copy <strong data-start="478" data-end="504">that entire key string</strong></p>
<p data-start="506" data-end="514">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="515" data-end="549"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>AIzaSyBabc123xyz456...</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="551" data-end="554">
<h1 data-section-id="ziez48" data-start="556" data-end="629"><span role="text">🔍 Case 2: If You Created a <strong data-start="586" data-end="605">Service Account</strong> (what you said earlier)</span></h1>
<p data-start="631" data-end="685">👉 Important:<br data-start="644" data-end="647">
<strong data-start="647" data-end="685">There is NO visible API key here ❌</strong></p>
<p data-start="687" data-end="726">Instead, you must download a JSON file.</p>
<hr data-start="728" data-end="731">
<h3 data-section-id="1876mp" data-start="733" data-end="756">📍 Where to get it:</h3>
<ol data-start="757" data-end="934">
<li data-section-id="1buxc1o" data-start="757" data-end="809">
<p data-start="760" data-end="809">Go to:<br data-start="766" data-end="769">
👉 <strong data-start="775" data-end="809">IAM &amp; Admin → Service Accounts</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1inosm2" data-start="810" data-end="841">
<p data-start="813" data-end="841">Click your service account</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kddywp" data-start="842" data-end="865">
<p data-start="845" data-end="865">Go to <strong data-start="851" data-end="865">“Keys” tab</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pp7m5w" data-start="866" data-end="917">
<p data-start="869" data-end="917">Click:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="882" data-end="917">Add Key → Create new key → JSON</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vyglzg" data-start="918" data-end="934">
<p data-start="921" data-end="934">Download file</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="936" data-end="939">
<h3 data-section-id="4q8b3s" data-start="941" data-end="961">📦 What you get:</h3>
<p data-start="962" data-end="974">A file like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="975" data-end="998"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>vision-key.json</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1000" data-end="1010">Inside it:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1011" data-end="1135"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JSON</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>{</span><br><span>  "type": </span><span class="ͼr">"service_account"</span><span>,</span><br><span>  "project_id": </span><span class="ͼr">"..."</span><span>,</span><br><span>  "private_key": </span><span class="ͼr">"-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----..."</span><span>,</span><br><span>  ...</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1137" data-end="1195">👉 This <strong data-start="1145" data-end="1195">JSON file = your credential (not a simple key)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1197" data-end="1200">
<h1 data-section-id="1a8nzvx" data-start="1202" data-end="1226">⚠️ Most Common Mistake</h1>
<p data-start="1227" data-end="1304">👉 Many people create a service account and then search for an API key — but:</p>
<ul data-start="1306" data-end="1366">
<li data-section-id="1fj0pso" data-start="1306" data-end="1337">
<p data-start="1308" data-end="1337">Service Account → JSON file</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ca1y0e" data-start="1338" data-end="1366">
<p data-start="1340" data-end="1366">API Key → visible string</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1368" data-end="1371">
<h1 data-section-id="1xtpnnl" data-start="1373" data-end="1410">🔥 What YOU should do (recommended)</h1>
<p data-start="1412" data-end="1438">Since your code uses this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1439" data-end="1470"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="