<p data-start="71" data-end="169">👉 <strong data-start="74" data-end="124">You don’t get an API key from Service Account.</strong><br data-start="124" data-end="127">
👉 You must <strong data-start="139" data-end="168">create a separate API key</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="171" data-end="174">
<h1 data-section-id="a0z1rh" data-start="176" data-end="232">✅ How to Create a Public API Key for Google Vision API</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="hwx3eo" data-start="234" data-end="270">🔹 Step 1: Go to Credentials Page</h2>
<p data-start="271" data-end="333">Open:<br data-start="276" data-end="279">
👉 <a data-start="282" data-end="331" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials">https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<hr data-start="335" data-end="338">
<h2 data-section-id="2r6qfc" data-start="340" data-end="380">🔹 Step 2: Click “Create Credentials”</h2>
<p data-start="381" data-end="400">At the top → click:</p>
<p data-start="402" data-end="453">👉 <strong data-start="405" data-end="429">+ CREATE CREDENTIALS</strong><br data-start="429" data-end="432">
👉 Select <strong data-start="442" data-end="453">API Key</strong></p>
<hr data-start="455" data-end="458">
<h2 data-section-id="q7y5k3" data-start="460" data-end="508">🔹 Step 3: Your API Key Will Appear Instantly</h2>
<p data-start="510" data-end="534">You’ll see a popup like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="536" data-end="599"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>AIzaSyAbCdEfGhIjKlMnOpQrStUvWxYz123456</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="601" data-end="655">👉 <strong data-start="604" data-end="628">THIS is your API key</strong><br data-start="628" data-end="631">
👉 Copy it immediately</p>
<hr data-start="657" data-end="660">
<h2 data-section-id="kxxxxs" data-start="662" data-end="713">🔹 Step 4: Enable Vision API (VERY IMPORTANT ⚠️)</h2>
<p data-start="715" data-end="747">If you skip this, it won’t work.</p>
<p data-start="749" data-end="830">Go to:<br data-start="755" data-end="758">
👉 <a data-start="761" data-end="828" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/vision.googleapis.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="832" data-end="854">Click:<br data-start="838" data-end="841">
👉 <strong data-start="844" data-end="854">ENABLE</strong></p>
<hr data-start="856" data-end="859">
<h2 data-section-id="3izumm" data-start="861" data-end="914">🔹 Step 5: (Optional but Recommended) Restrict Key</h2>
<p data-start="916" data-end="964">Click your API key → under <strong data-start="943" data-end="963">API restrictions</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="965" data-end="1022">
<li data-section-id="56rgnl" data-start="965" data-end="991">
<p data-start="967" data-end="991">Select: <strong data-start="975" data-end="991">Restrict key</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="g3w16q" data-start="992" data-end="1022">
<p data-start="994" data-end="1022">Choose: <strong data-start="1002" data-end="1022">Cloud Vision API</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1024" data-end="1027">
<h1 data-section-id="zt50av" data-start="1029" data-end="1054">✅ Where to Use This Key</h1>
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1069">In your code:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1071" data-end="1158"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="