<h1 data-section-id="1xh1yri" data-start="1261" data-end="1292">❗ Common Issues (Check These)</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="1g1pk7b" data-start="1294" data-end="1319">❌ “API key not found”</h3>
<p data-start="1320" data-end="1380">👉 You didn’t create API key — you created service account</p>
<h3 data-section-id="6tdtl3" data-start="1382" data-end="1407">❌ “Permission denied”</h3>
<p data-start="1408" data-end="1435">👉 Vision API not enabled</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1q1ih2o" data-start="1437" data-end="1464">❌ “Billing not enabled”</h3>
<p data-start="1465" data-end="1512">👉 You must enable billing (Google requires it)</p>
<hr data-start="1514" data-end="1517">
<h1 data-section-id="gt6exd" data-start="1519" data-end="1549">🔥 Fastest Fix (Do This Now)</h1>
