<p data-start="136" data-end="176">Now the next logical section is usually:</p>
<h1 data-section-id="88f51k" data-start="178" data-end="221"><span role="text">✅ <strong data-start="182" data-end="221">Related Work (Based on Your Papers)</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="223" data-end="268">Here’s a <strong data-start="232" data-end="265">clean, ready-to-use paragraph</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="270" data-end="273">
<h2 data-section-id="gwxf5e" data-start="275" data-end="293">📄 Related Work</h2>
<p data-start="295" data-end="694">Several research studies have explored the use of <strong data-start="345" data-end="404">OCR and AI techniques for medical prescription analysis</strong>. Existing works primarily focus on extracting text from handwritten prescriptions using machine learning and deep learning models. Transformer-based models such as TrOCR and other OCR techniques have shown promising results in recognizing handwritten medical text with improved accuracy.</p>
<p data-start="696" data-end="986">Some studies further extend this by applying <strong data-start="741" data-end="778">natural language processing (NLP)</strong> to identify medicine names and dosage patterns. Additionally, research in medical informatics highlights the importance of converting unstructured medical data into structured formats for better usability.</p>
<p data-start="988" data-end="1254">However, most of these systems are limited to <strong data-start="1034" data-end="1066">text extraction and analysis</strong>, without providing user-friendly explanations or real-time assistance. They also lack integration with <strong data-start="1170" data-end="1217">reminder systems and accessibility features</strong>, especially for rural populations.</p>
<p data-start="1256" data-end="1457">The proposed system addresses these limitations by combining OCR, NLP, and AI-based interpretation to deliver <strong data-start="1366" data-end="1413">clear instructions and medication reminders</strong>, making it more practical and user-centric.</p>
<hr data-start="1459" data-end="1462">
<h2 data-section-id="zeugwr" data-start="1464" data-end="1495">🎯 Short Version (if needed)</h2>
<p data-start="1497" data-end="1720">👉 <em data-start="1500" data-end="1720">Existing systems use OCR and NLP to extract and process prescription data, but they lack user-friendly interpretation, real-time assistance, and accessibility for rural users, which the proposed system aims to address.</em></p>
<hr data-start="1722" data-end="1725">
<h2 data-section-id="1cl6mtp" data-start="1727" data-end="1752">⚡ What You Can Do Next</h2>
