uding:<br data-start="68" data-end="71">
✅ Research papers (relevant)<br data-start="99" data-end="102">
✅ Literature survey<br data-start="121" data-end="124">
✅ Flaws<br data-start="131" data-end="134">
✅ Research gaps</p>
<p data-start="153" data-end="188">All are <strong data-start="161" data-end="185">ready for report/PPT</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="190" data-end="193">
<h1 data-section-id="128sd1k" data-start="195" data-end="251">✅ 📚 Selected Research Papers (Relevant to Your Topic)</h1>
<ol data-start="253" data-end="586">
<li data-section-id="16i74i5" data-start="253" data-end="316">
<p data-start="256" data-end="316"><strong data-start="256" data-end="314">Image-Based Prescription Information Extraction (2024)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1di7lq0" data-start="317" data-end="375">
<p data-start="320" data-end="375"><strong data-start="320" data-end="373">OCR + YOLO-based Prescription Digitization (2025)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nogt6c" data-start="376" data-end="457">
<p data-start="379" data-end="457"><strong data-start="379" data-end="455">Medical Text Extraction &amp; Classification from Prescription Images (IEEE)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q21n9l" data-start="458" data-end="527">
<p data-start="461" data-end="527"><strong data-start="461" data-end="525">AI-Based OCR for Handwritten Prescription Recognition (2025)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p8zzyl" data-start="528" data-end="586">
<p data-start="531" data-end="586"><strong data-start="531" data-end="584">Algorithms for Prescription Digitalization (2021)</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="588" data-end="591">
<h1 data-section-id="1a1npaf" data-start="593" data-end="617">✅ 📖 Literature Survey</h1>
<p data-start="619" data-end="757">Existing research focuses on using <strong data-start="654" data-end="679">OCR and AI techniques</strong> to digitize handwritten medical prescriptions and extract useful information.</p>
<ul data-start="759" data-end="1644">
<li data-section-id="b24pj5" data-start="759" data-end="952">
<p data-start="761" data-end="952">Many studies use <strong data-start="778" data-end="804">image processing + OCR</strong> to convert prescription images into digital text, achieving high accuracy (~98%) in controlled environments <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 70px;"><a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877050924007786?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877050924007786?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 70px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">ScienceDirect</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nc4d1p" data-start="953" data-end="1154">
<p data-start="955" data-end="1154">Advanced systems combine <strong data-start="980" data-end="1016">object detection (YOLO) with OCR</strong> to identify important regions such as medicine names and dosage, improving extraction performance <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 70px;"><a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0010482525001623?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0010482525001623?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 70px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">ScienceDirect</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="or9f2h" data-start="1155" data-end="1326">
<p data-start="1157" data-end="1326">Some works integrate <strong data-start="1178" data-end="1204">NLP models (like BERT)</strong> to classify extracted text into categories such as medicines, symptoms, and tests <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 71px;"><a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/368998931_Medical_Text_Extraction_and_Classification_from_Prescription_Images?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/368998931_Medical_Text_Extraction_and_Classification_from_Prescription_Images?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 71px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">ResearchGate</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="18du9fz" data-start="1327" data-end="1481">
<p data-start="1329" data-end="1481">Deep learning approaches (CNN, LSTM, Transformers) are widely used to handle <strong data-start="1406" data-end="1441">complex handwriting recognition</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 71px;"><a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/395110562_AI-Based_OCR_System_for_Handwritten_Medical_Prescription_Recognition_and_Interpretation?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/395110562_AI-Based_OCR_System_for_Handwritten_Medical_Prescription_Recognition_and_Interpretation?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 71px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">ResearchGate</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8hlu1m" data-start="1482" data-end="1644">
<p data-start="1484" data-end="1644">Algorithm-based methods improve efficiency by reducing unnecessary word matching and speeding up prescription processing <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 70px;"><a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2468502X21000334?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2468502X21000334?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 70px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">ScienceDirect</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1646" data-end="1740">👉 Overall, research shows that <strong data-start="1678" data-end="1696">OCR + AI + NLP</strong> is effective for prescription digitization.</p>
<hr data-start="1742" data-end="1745">
<h1 data-section-id="axczig" data-start="1747" data-end="1777">❌ Flaws in Existing Research</h1>
<ul data-start="1779" data-end="2287">
<li data-section-id="gudubm" data-start="1779" data-end="1866">
<p data-start="1781" data-end="1866">Most systems are tested in <strong data-start="1808" data-end="1831">controlled datasets</strong>, not real-world rural conditions</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="s2rwho" data-start="1867" data-end="1974">
<p data-start="1869" data-end="1974">Difficulty in handling <strong data-start="1892" data-end="1934">poor handwriting and irregular spacing</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 38px;"><a href="https://www.aimsciences.org/article/doi/10.3934/jdg.2026016?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.aimsciences.org/article/doi/10.3934/jdg.2026016?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 38px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">AIMS</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wnmsdp" data-start="1975" data-end="2031">
<p data-start="1977" data-end="2031">Limited support for <strong data-start="1997" data-end="2029">multi-language prescriptions</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tysdlf" data-start="2032" data-end="2081">
<p data-start="2034" data-end="2081">High dependency on <strong data-start="2053" data-end="2079">large labeled datasets</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m50lgz" data-start="2082" data-end="2148">
<p data-start="2084" data-end="2148">OCR errors still lead to <strong data-start="2109" data-end="2146">incorrect medicine interpretation</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vbe4i6" data-start="2149" data-end="2215">
<p data-start="2151" data-end="2215">Lack of <strong data-start="2159" data-end="2213">user-friendly output (simple language explanation)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="b41jic" data-start="2216" data-end="2287">
<p data-start="2218" data-end="2287">Systems are often <strong data-start="2236" data-end="2285">complex and not lightweight for real-time use</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2289" data-end="2292">
<h1 data-section-id="4syaut" data-start="2294" data-end="2312">⚠️ Research Gaps</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1ypbioq" data-start="2314" data-end="2334">🔴 Technical Gaps</h2>
<ul data-start="2335" data-end="2634">
<li data-section-id="1q3tt87" data-start="2335" data-end="2414">
<p data-start="2337" data-end="2414">No fully reliable solution for <strong data-start="2368" data-end="2412">highly unclear handwritten prescriptions</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f8zml5" data-start="2415" data-end="2510">
<p data-start="2417" data-end="2510">Limited ability to extract <strong data-start="2444" data-end="2508">complete context (medicine + dosage + instructions together)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sgc2at" data-start="2511" data-end="2581">
<p data-start="2513" data-end="2581">Poor performance in <strong data-start="2533" data-end="2579">low-quality images (blur, lighting issues)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ama35" data-start="2582" data-end="2634">
<p data-start="2584" data-end="2634">Lack of <strong data-start="2592" data-end="2634">multi-language and regional adaptation</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2636" data-end="2639">
<h2 data-section-id="19x208z" data-start="2641" data-end="2664">🟠 System-Level Gaps</h2>
<ul data-start="2665" data-end="2850">
<li data-section-id="1dibobv" data-start="2665" data-end="2731">
<p data-start="2667" data-end="2731">No <strong data-start="2670" data-end="2691">end-to-end system</strong> (OCR → understanding → user guidance)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17nl6ri" data-start="2732" data-end="2779">
<p data-start="2734" data-end="2779">Most works stop at <strong data-start="2753" data-end="2777">text extraction only</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fcvmst" data-start="2780" data-end="2850">
<p data-start="2782" data-end="2850">No integration with <strong data-start="2802" data-end="2848">real-time applications (API-based systems)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2852" data-end="2855">
<h2 data-section-id="1c8kiu2" data-start="2857" data-end="2914">🟢 User-Centric Gaps (MOST IMPORTANT FOR YOUR PROJECT)</h2>
<ul data-start="2915" data-end="3159">
<li data-section-id="5299vf" data-start="2915" data-end="2964">
<p data-start="2917" data-end="2964">No focus on <strong data-start="2929" data-end="2962">rural users and accessibility</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1u56uji" data-start="2965" data-end="3033">
<p data-start="2967" data-end="3033">No <strong data-start="2970" data-end="3009">simple explanation of prescriptions</strong> for non-medical users</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uw3a2r" data-start="3034" data-end="3093">
<p data-start="3036" data-end="3093">No <strong data-start="3039" data-end="3091">reminder/notification system for medicine intake</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oo6rm3" data-start="3094" data-end="3159">
<p data-start="3096" data-end="3159">No support for <strong data-start="3111" data-end="3157">low-tech environments (mobile-first usage)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3161" data-end="3164">
<h1 data-section-id="jldhgn" data-start="3166" data-end="3211">🎯 Final Gap Statement (USE THIS IN REPORT)</h1>
<p data-start="3213" data-end="3484">👉 <em data-start="3216" data-end="3484">“Existing research primarily focuses on extracting text from handwritten prescriptions using OCR and AI, but lacks an end-to-end, user-centric solution that converts prescriptions into simple instructions with real-time assistance, especially for rural populations.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="3486" data-end="3489">
