</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2235" data-end="2238">
<h1 data-section-id="1a1npaf" data-start="2240" data-end="2264">✅ 📖 Literature Survey</h1>
<p data-start="2266" data-end="2388">Research in this domain primarily focuses on <strong data-start="2311" data-end="2387">digitizing handwritten medical prescriptions using OCR and AI techniques</strong>.</p>
<ul data-start="2390" data-end="3281">
<li data-section-id="293x0n" data-start="2390" data-end="2582">
<p data-start="2392" data-end="2582">Traditional approaches rely on <strong data-start="2423" data-end="2464">OCR combined with image preprocessing</strong> to extract prescription text with high accuracy under controlled conditions <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 70px;"><a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877050924007786?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1877050924007786?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 70px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">ScienceDirect</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15yl0m5" data-start="2583" data-end="2765">
<p data-start="2585" data-end="2765">Deep learning models such as <strong data-start="2614" data-end="2639">CNN, LSTM, and BiLSTM</strong> are widely used for recognizing complex handwriting patterns and improving accuracy <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 49px;"><a href="https://www.ijcaonline.org/archives/volume187/number45/interpreting-doctors-notes-handwriting-recognition-deep-learning/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.ijcaonline.org/archives/volume187/number45/interpreting-doctors-notes-handwriting-recognition-deep-learning/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 49px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">IJCA</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5hecjp" data-start="2766" data-end="2950">
<p data-start="2768" data-end="2950">Recent advancements include <strong data-start="2796" data-end="2835">Transformer-based models like TrOCR</strong>, which significantly improve performance in recognizing handwritten text <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 46px;"><a href="https://jcbi.org/index.php/Main/article/view/1054?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://jcbi.org/index.php/Main/article/view/1054?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 46px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">jcbi.org</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1l4nljn" data-start="2951" data-end="3114">
<p data-start="2953" data-end="3114">Some studies incorporate <strong data-start="2978" data-end="3011">object detection (Mask R-CNN)</strong> to identify specific regions like medicine names and dosages <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.18199?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s1vvue" data-start="3115" data-end="3281">
<p data-start="3117" data-end="3281">Emerging research explores <strong data-start="3144" data-end="3183">multimodal AI and LLM-based systems</strong> to better understand prescription context and structure <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 37px;"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.09729?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.09729?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 37px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">arXiv</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3283" data-end="3392">👉 Overall, literature shows that combining <strong data-start="3327" data-end="3356">OCR + Deep Learning + NLP</strong> improves prescription digitization.</p>
<hr data-start="3394" data-end="3397">
<h1 data-section-id="qulfn8" data-start="3399" data-end="3427">❌ Flaws in Existing Papers</h1>
<ul data-start="3429" data-end="3922">
<li data-section-id="1ne441" data-start="3429" data-end="3493">
<p data-start="3431" data-end="3493">Models perform well only on <strong data-start="3459" data-end="3491">clean or controlled datasets</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vwaskq" data-start="3494" data-end="3600">
<p data-start="3496" data-end="3600">Difficulty handling <strong data-start="3516" data-end="3558">poor handwriting and irregular formats</strong> <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 38px;"><a href="https://www.aimsciences.org/article/doi/10.3934/jdg.2026016?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.aimsciences.org/article/doi/10.3934/jdg.2026016?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 38px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">AIMS</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tysdlf" data-start="3601" data-end="3650">
<p data-start="3603" data-end="3650">High dependency on <strong data-start="3622" data-end="3648">large labeled datasets</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="asqkkg" data-start="3651" data-end="3725">
<p data-start="3653" data-end="3725">Many systems extract <strong data-start="3674" data-end="3723">only partial information (medicine OR dosage)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wnmsdp" data-start="3726" data-end="3782">
<p data-start="3728" data-end="3782">Limited support for <strong data-start="3748" data-end="3780">multi-language prescriptions</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cypfhd" data-start="3783" data-end="3860">
<p data-start="3785" data-end="3860">Complex architectures → <strong data-start="3809" data-end="3858">not suitable for real-time or lightweight use</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cdpyau" data-start="3861" data-end="3922">
<p data-start="3863" data-end="3922">OCR errors still lead to <strong data-start="3888" data-end="3920">wrong medical interpretation</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3924" data-end="3927">
<h1 data-section-id="4syaut" data-start="3929" data-end="3947">⚠️ Research Gaps</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1ypbioq" data-start="3949" data-end="3969">🔴 Technical Gaps</h2>
<ul data-start="3970" data-end="4137">
<li data-section-id="1w1bdy" data-start="3970" data-end="4029">
<p data-start="3972" data-end="4029">No reliable system for <strong data-start="3995" data-end="4027">highly illegible handwriting</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cdqbvz" data-start="4030" data-end="4093">
<p data-start="4032" data-end="4093">Poor performance in <strong data-start="4052" data-end="4091">low-quality images (blur, lighting)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1l1m4b4" data-start="4094" data-end="4137">
<p data-start="4096" data-end="4137">Lack of <strong data-start="4104" data-end="4135">multi-language adaptability</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4139" data-end="4142">
<h2 data-section-id="ge4a7s" data-start="4144" data-end="4161">🟠 System Gaps</h2>
<ul data-start="4162" data-end="4338">
<li data-section-id="1gh3fby" data-start="4162" data-end="4210">
<p data-start="4164" data-end="4210">Most works focus only on <strong data-start="4189" data-end="4208">text extraction</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="y5vuwl" data-start="4211" data-end="4272">
<p data-start="4213" data-end="4272">No <strong data-start="4216" data-end="4270">end-to-end pipeline (OCR → understanding → action)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i0izss" data-start="4273" data-end="4338">
<p data-start="4275" data-end="4338">Limited integration with <strong data-start="4300" data-end="4336">real-world APIs and applications</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4340" data-end="4343">
<h2 data-section-id="133dyw5" data-start="4345" data-end="4385">🟢 User-Centric Gaps (MOST IMPORTANT)</h2>
<ul data-start="4386" data-end="4565">
<li data-section-id="1eeaowu" data-start="4386" data-end="4417">
<p data-start="4388" data-end="4417">No focus on <strong data-start="4400" data-end="4415">rural users</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nlva0e" data-start="4418" data-end="4464">
<p data-start="4420" data-end="4464">No <strong data-start="4423" data-end="4462">simple explanation of prescriptions</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nzgvhc" data-start="4465" data-end="4504">
<p data-start="4467" data-end="4504">No <strong data-start="4470" data-end="4502">reminder/notification system</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s6tajp" data-start="4505" data-end="4565">
<p data-start="4507" data-end="4565">No support for <strong data-start="4522" data-end="4563">low-tech users (non-English speakers)</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4567" data-end="4570">
<h1 data-section-id="117jcyb" data-start="4572" data-end="4605">🎯 Final Research Gap Statement</h1>
<p data-start="4607" data-end="4870">👉 <em data-start="4610" data-end="4870">“While existing research effectively extracts text from handwritten prescriptions using OCR and deep learning, it lacks a complete, user-centric system that simplifies medical instructions and provides real-time assistance, especially for rural populations.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="4872" data-end="4875">
