<li data-section-id="76z8b2" data-start="5000" data-end="5030">
<p data-start="5002" data-end="5030">✔ Adds <strong data-start="5009" data-end="5028">reminders (NEW)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ysqq1i" data-start="5031" data-end="5069">
<p data-start="5033" data-end="5069">✔ Targets <strong data-start="5043" data-end="5067">rural users (UNIQUE)</strong></p>
