<h3 data-section-id="1ycrvhh" data-start="1244" data-end="1266">3️⃣ Run prediction</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1267" data-end="1309"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>python predict.py</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1311" data-end="1314">
<h1 data-section-id="1677fjl" data-start="1316" data-end="1364">❗ Limitations (VERY IMPORTANT FOR YOUR REPORT)</h1>
<ul data-start="1366" data-end="1582">
<li data-section-id="gbitpi" data-start="1366" data-end="1418">
<p data-start="1368" data-end="1418">Works at <strong data-start="1377" data-end="1416">character level (not full sentence)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="l0m53h" data-start="1419" data-end="1454">
<p data-start="1421" data-end="1454">Requires <strong data-start="1430" data-end="1452">clean segmentation</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1k0kjhk" data-start="1455" data-end="1504">
<p data-start="1457" data-end="1504">Not accurate for <strong data-start="1474" data-end="1502">real messy prescriptions</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rg7zmy" data-start="1505" data-end="1582">
<p data-start="1507" data-end="1527">No understanding of:</p>
<ul data-start="1530" data-end="1582">
<li data-section-id="1acvd6z" data-start="1530" data-end="1550">
<p data-start="1532" data-end="1550">medicine meaning</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cfyoz7" data-start="1553" data-end="1563">
<p data-start="1555" data-end="1563">dosage</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="x2hm77" data-start="1566" data-end="1582">
<p data-start="1568" data-end="1582">instructions</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1584" data-end="1587">
<h1 data-section-id="y19nhf" data-start="1589" data-end="1624">⚠️ Research Gap from This Project</h1>
<p data-start="1626" data-end="1790">👉 <em data-start="1629" data-end="1790">“The model focuses only on character recognition using CNN and lacks contextual understanding, making it insufficient for interpreting complete prescriptions.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="1792" data-end="1795">
<h1 data-section-id="ozqpkf" data-start="1797" data-end="1822">🎯 How You Can Use This</h1>
<p data-start="1824" data-end="1843">👉 In your project:</p>
<ul data-start="1844" data-end="1970">
<li data-section-id="1uelsy5" data-start="1844" data-end="1898">
<p data-start="1846" data-end="1898">Use this as <strong data-start="1858" data-end="1896">reference (trained model approach)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="134nq9z" data-start="1899" data-end="1970">
<p data-start="1901" data-end="1919">Compare with your:</p>
<ul data-start="1922" data-end="1970">
<li data-section-id="1nekc7m" data-start="1922" data-end="1939">
<p data-start="1924" data-end="1939">API-based OCR</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12a1j6b" data-start="1942" data-end="1970">
<p data-start="1944" data-end="1970">LLM-based interpretation</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1972" data-end="1975">
<h1 data-section-id="u1jdtu" data-start="1977" data-end="2009">🔥 Best Way to Explain in Viva</h1>
<p data-start="2011" data-end="2196">👉 <em data-start="2014" data-end="2196">“Existing CNN-based models perform character-level recognition but fail to interpret full prescriptions, which is why our system uses advanced OCR and AI for better understanding.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="2198" data-end="2201">
