ut I’ll show you <strong data-start="97" data-end="143">exactly how to get it yourself in 1 minute</strong> 👍</p>
<hr data-start="148" data-end="151">
<h1 data-section-id="lcefix" data-start="153" data-end="197">✅ How to Get the Model File from That Repo</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="6hyt1v" data-start="199" data-end="226">🔗 Step 1: Open the Repo</h2>
<p data-start="227" data-end="293">👉 Go here:<br data-start="238" data-end="241">
<a data-start="241" data-end="293" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/sanketnaik99/doctors-prescription">https://github.com/sanketnaik99/doctors-prescription<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<hr data-start="295" data-end="298">
<h2 data-section-id="fd0ted" data-start="300" data-end="333">📂 Step 2: Look for Model File</h2>
<p data-start="335" data-end="369">In the repo, check for files like:</p>
<ul data-start="370" data-end="420">
<li data-section-id="1398gr8" data-start="370" data-end="384">
<p data-start="372" data-end="384"><code data-start="372" data-end="382">model.h5</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14fa1zc" data-start="385" data-end="403">
<p data-start="387" data-end="403"><code data-start="387" data-end="401">cnn_model.h5</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1l5mx3c" data-start="404" data-end="420">
<p data-start="406" data-end="420"><code data-start="406" data-end="418">weights.h5</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="422" data-end="436">👉 If present:</p>
<ul data-start="437" data-end="478">
<li data-section-id="2d6li1" data-start="437" data-end="455">
<p data-start="439" data-end="455">Click the file</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nojqvm" data-start="456" data-end="478">
<p data-start="458" data-end="478">Click <strong data-start="464" data-end="476">Download</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="480" data-end="483">
<h2 data-section-id="m6rkkh" data-start="485" data-end="530">❗ If Model File is NOT There (Very Common)</h2>
<p data-start="532" data-end="613">Most repos <strong data-start="543" data-end="571">don’t upload model files</strong> (because they are large).<br data-start="597" data-end="600">
In that case:</p>
<p data-start="615" data-end="651">👉 You need to <strong data-start="630" data-end="651">train it yourself</strong></p>
<hr data-start="653" data-end="656">
<h1 data-section-id="ef447n" data-start="658" data-end="692">✅ How to Generate the Model File</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="iumoe1" data-start="694" data-end="720">▶️ Run training script</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="721" data-end="748"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>python train.py</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="750" data-end="753">
<h3 data-section-id="1o4s2vt" data-start="755" data-end="776">📦 After training</h3>
<p data-start="777" data-end="792">It will create:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="793" data-end="813"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>model.h5</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="815" data-end="849">👉 That is your trained model file</p>
<hr data-start="851" data-end="854">
<h1 data-section-id="r7nad" data-start="856" data-end="891">⚡ Faster Trick (Skip Training 😏)</h1>
<p data-start="893" data-end="920">If you don’t want to train:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1dm46ru" data-start="922" data-end="971">👉 Modify code to load pretrained OCR instead</h3>
<p data-start="972" data-end="994">Replace CNN part with:</p>
<ul data-start="995" data-end="1029">
<li data-section-id="1l6ewit" data-start="995" data-end="1007">
