</li>
<li data-section-id="3yfxwd" data-start="1008" data-end="1029">
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1029">Google Vision API</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1031" data-end="1034">
<h1 data-section-id="v7yn3i" data-start="1036" data-end="1083">🔥 If You REALLY Need a Model File (Shortcut)</h1>
