<p data-start="1444" data-end="1475">OR <strong data-start="1447" data-end="1473">TrOCR pretrained model</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1477" data-end="1480">
<h1 data-section-id="akzrmp" data-start="1482" data-end="1500">💡 Best Strategy</h1>
<p data-start="1502" data-end="1521">For your hackathon:</p>
<ul data-start="1522" data-end="1601">
