<hr data-start="661" data-end="664">
<h2 data-section-id="1imfprx" data-start="666" data-end="698">🔹 3. Check Dataset Structure</h2>
<p data-start="700" data-end="744">Inside the repo, dataset usually looks like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="746" data-end="812"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>dataset/</span><br><span>   ├── A/</span><br><span>   ├── B/</span><br><span>   ├── C/</span><br><span>   ├── 0/</span><br><span>   ├── 1/</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="814" data-end="894">👉 Each folder = <strong data-start="831" data-end="852">label (character)</strong><br data-start="852" data-end="855">
👉 Images inside = <strong data-start="874" data-end="894">training samples</strong></p>
<hr data-start="896" data-end="899">
<h2 data-section-id="1vj6bv4" data-start="901" data-end="936">🔹 4. Understand Training Script</h2>
<p data-start="938" data-end="953">Open <code data-start="943" data-end="953">train.py</code></p>
<p data-start="955" data-end="963">It will:</p>
