<hr data-start="1591" data-end="1594">
<h1 data-section-id="pkxim9" data-start="1596" data-end="1635">🔥 IMPORTANT (Very Important Insight)</h1>
<p data-start="1637" data-end="1654">👉 This model is:</p>
<ul data-start="1655" data-end="1714">
<li data-section-id="c0lzt9" data-start="1655" data-end="1674">
<p data-start="1657" data-end="1674">Character-based</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j0l62y" data-start="1675" data-end="1714">
<p data-start="1677" data-end="1714">NOT full prescription understanding</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1716" data-end="1719">So:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1720" data-end="1778"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Prescription → Split → Letters → Predict → Combine</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1780" data-end="1820">👉 That’s why accuracy drops in real use</p>
<hr data-start="1822" data-end="1825">
<h1 data-section-id="k4in4q" data-start="1827" data-end="1866">🎯 Better Training Upgrade (Optional)</h1>
<p data-start="1868" data-end="1895">If you want stronger model:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="g16f1b" data-start="1897" data-end="1923">Instead of characters:</h3>
<p data-start="1924" data-end="1933">Train on:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1934" data-end="1977"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>"Paracetamol"</span><br><span>"Amoxicillin"</span><br><span>"1-0-1"</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1979" data-end="2015">👉 Word-level training = much better</p>
<hr data-start="2017" data-end="2020">
<h1 data-section-id="1eypwzf" data-start="2022" data-end="2050">🚀 Best Advice (Hackathon)</h1>
<p data-start="2052" data-end="2063">👉 DO THIS:</p>
<ul data-start="2065" data-end="2124">
<li data-section-id="x2f386" data-start="2065" data-end="2090">
<p data-start="2067" data-end="2090">Train once (for demo)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="6and9u" data-start="2091" data-end="2124">
<p data-start="2093" data-end="2124">Use API OCR (for real output)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2126" data-end="2146">👉 Then say in viva:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2147" data-end="2244">
<p data-start="2149" data-end="2244">“We experimented with CNN-based training, but used OCR APIs for better real-world performance.”</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2246" data-end="2249">
<h1 data-section-id="1edadv0" data-start="2251" data-end="2271">⚡ One-Line Summary</h1>
<p data-start="2273" data-end="2437">👉 <em data-start="2276" data-end="2437">“The dataset is trained by feeding labeled character images into a CNN model, which learns to recognize patterns and outputs predictions saved as a .h5 model.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="2439" data-end="2442">
<p data-start="2444" data-end="2605" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want next:<br>
