>, (</span><span class="ͼq">64</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">64</span><span>))</span><br><span class="ͼt">img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">255.0</span><br><span class="ͼt">img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">img</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>reshape(</span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">64</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">64</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">prediction</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">model</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>predict(</span><span class="ͼt">img</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼt">print</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">prediction</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="736" data-end="767">👉 Check if output is correct ✅</p>
<hr data-start="769" data-end="772">
<h2 data-section-id="g00u9k" data-start="774" data-end="809">🔹 3. Convert Prediction to Text</h2>
<p data-start="811" data-end="827">If labels exist:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="829" data-end="956"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">labels</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> [</span><span class="ͼr">'A'</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼr">'B'</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼr">'C'</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼr">'0'</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼr">'1'</span><span>]  </span><span class="ͼl"># example</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">predicted_class</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">labels</span><span>[</span><span class="ͼt">np</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>argmax(</span><span class="ͼt">prediction</span><span>)]</span><br><span class="ͼt">print</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">predicted_class</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="958" data-end="961">
<h2 data-section-id="ap03x7" data-start="963" data-end="1003">🔹 4. Build Full Pipeline (Important)</h2>
<p data-start="1005" data-end="1054">Right now model predicts <strong data-start="1030" data-end="1052">one character only</strong></p>
<p data-start="1056" data-end="1068">👉 You must:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1070" data-end="1206"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Prescription Image</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Preprocessing</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Character Segmentation</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Model Prediction (each char)</span><br><span>   ↓</span><br><span>Combine → Full Text</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1208" data-end="1211">
<h2 data-section-id="bwrhbj" data-start="1213" data-end="1249">🔹 5. Integrate with Your Project</h2>
<p data-start="1251" data-end="1281">Now connect it to your system:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="sx4rs2" data-start="1283" data-end="1312">Option A: FastAPI Backend</h3>
<ul data-start="1313" data-end="1392">
<li data-section-id="jgu5eu" data-start="1313" data-end="1332">
<p data-start="1315" data-end="1332">Load model once</p>
</li>
