<h1 data-section-id="1nfpz23" data-start="84" data-end="142">✅ 🔗 How to Add Shared Google Drive Folder to “My Drive”</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1tbyldp" data-start="144" data-end="172">🔹 Step 1: Open Your Link</h2>
<p data-start="173" data-end="194">Open this in browser:</p>
<p data-start="196" data-end="271">👉 <a data-start="199" data-end="271" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Ij44uXg9TBbyJJC5bmwmc8jjqEOVY6_s">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Ij44uXg9TBbyJJC5bmwmc8jjqEOVY6_s<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<hr data-start="273" data-end="276">
<h2 data-section-id="peshbe" data-start="278" data-end="304">🔹 Step 2: Add Shortcut</h2>
<p data-start="306" data-end="320">Once it opens:</p>
<ol data-start="322" data-end="444">
<li data-section-id="5hk34" data-start="322" data-end="365">
<p data-start="325" data-end="365">At the top, you’ll see the folder name</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1odya0j" data-start="366" data-end="444">
<p data-start="369" data-end="444">Click the <strong data-start="379" data-end="411">“Add shortcut to Drive” icon</strong> (looks like a Drive logo with +)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="446" data-end="518">👉 OR right-click on the folder →<br data-start="479" data-end="482">
👉 Click <strong data-start="491" data-end="518">“Add shortcut to Drive”</strong></p>
<hr data-start="520" data-end="523">
<h2 data-section-id="1gxss2i" data-start="525" data-end="554">🔹 Step 3: Choose Location</h2>
<p data-start="556" data-end="576">A popup will appear:</p>
<ul data-start="578" data-end="625">
<li data-section-id="10vmysi" data-start="578" data-end="600">
<p data-start="580" data-end="600">Select: <strong data-start="588" data-end="600">My Drive</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="n9jwtz" data-start="601" data-end="625">
<p data-start="603" data-end="625">Click <strong data-start="609" data-end="625">Add Shortcut</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="627" data-end="630">
<h2 data-section-id="1461t0v" data-start="632" data-end="653">🔹 Step 4: Confirm</h2>
<p data-start="655" data-end="665">Now go to:</p>
<p data-start="667" data-end="711">👉 <a data-start="670" data-end="709" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/my-drive">https://drive.google.com/drive/my-drive<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="713" data-end="747">You should see your folder there ✅</p>
<hr data-start="749" data-end="752">
