<hr data-start="72" data-end="75">
<h1 data-section-id="mdg045" data-start="77" data-end="111">✅ Which Accuracy Should You Use?</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="13edrx8" data-start="113" data-end="132">🎯 Final Answer:</h2>
<p data-start="133" data-end="166">👉 <strong data-start="136" data-end="166">Use: VALIDATION ACCURACY ✅</strong></p>
<hr data-start="168" data-end="171">
<h1 data-section-id="cwvhd" data-start="173" data-end="182">🧠 Why?</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1wze13i" data-start="184" data-end="227">🔹 1. Training Accuracy (Epoch Accuracy)</h2>
<ul data-start="228" data-end="294">
<li data-section-id="12vtq04" data-start="228" data-end="259">
<p data-start="230" data-end="259">Accuracy on <strong data-start="242" data-end="259">training data</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11g4kk0" data-start="260" data-end="294">
<p data-start="262" data-end="294">Model has already seen this data</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="296" data-end="307">👉 Problem:</p>
<ul data-start="308" data-end="347">
<li data-section-id="a8ttvd" data-start="308" data-end="329">
<p data-start="310" data-end="329">Can be <strong data-start="317" data-end="329">too high</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ho3lyg" data-start="330" data-end="347">
<p data-start="332" data-end="347">May <strong data-start="336" data-end="347">overfit</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="349" data-end="352">
<h2 data-section-id="inydn0" data-start="354" data-end="394">🔹 2. Validation Accuracy (IMPORTANT)</h2>
<ul data-start="395" data-end="453">
<li data-section-id="9aqv1e" data-start="395" data-end="424">
<p data-start="397" data-end="424">Accuracy on <strong data-start="409" data-end="424">unseen data</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jdy13j" data-start="425" data-end="453">
<p data-start="427" data-end="453">Tests <strong data-start="433" data-end="453">real performance</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="455" data-end="496">👉 This is what matters in real-world use</p>
<hr data-start="498" data-end="501">
<h1 data-section-id="wknvcp" data-start="503" data-end="515">📊 Example</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="517" data-end="588"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Epoch 10:</span><br><span>Training Accuracy = 98%</span><br><span>Validation Accuracy = 86%</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="590" data-end="611">👉 You should report:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="612" data-end="644"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Model Accuracy = 86%</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="646" data-end="649">
<h1 data-section-id="z8xni0" data-start="651" data-end="682">⚠️ Why Not Training Accuracy?</h1>
<p data-start="684" data-end="695">👉 Because:</p>
<ul data-start="696" data-end="760">
<li data-section-id="3gzmd" data-start="696" data-end="725">
<p data-start="698" data-end="725">Model can <strong data-start="708" data-end="725">memorize data</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16bn3ej" data-start="726" data-end="760">
<p data-start="728" data-end="760">Doesn’t reflect real performance</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="762" data-end="765">
<h1 data-section-id="1tv9g49" data-start="767" data-end="793">🔥 What Examiners Expect</h1>
<p data-start="795" data-end="809">When they ask:</p>
<p data-start="811" data-end="844">👉 “What is your model accuracy?”</p>
<p data-start="846" data-end="854">You say:</p>
<p data-start="856" data-end="964">👉 <em data-start="859" data-end="964">“The model achieved around <strong data-start="887" data-end="914">86% validation accuracy</strong>, which reflects its performance on unseen data.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="966" data-end="969">
<h1 data-section-id="icq5wa" data-start="971" data-end="1013">🧪 Extra (If You Want to Sound Smart 😏)</h1>
<p data-start="1015" data-end="1027">👉 Add this:</p>
<ul data-start="1029" data-end="1119">
<li data-section-id="1wqxjkx" data-start="1029" data-end="1119">
<p data-start="1031" data-end="1119">“Training accuracy was higher, but we rely on validation accuracy to avoid overfitting.”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1121" data-end="1124">
<h1 data-section-id="1pej2iw" data-start="1126" data-end="1144">📈 Best Practice</h1>
<p data-start="1146" data-end="1157">Also check:</p>
<ul data-start="1159" data-end="1255">
<li data-section-id="6zahem" data-start="1159" data-end="1214">
<p data-start="1161" data-end="1214">If training ↑ but validation ↓<br data-start="1191" data-end="1194">
👉 Overfitting ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kmqbz4" data-start="1216" data-end="1255">
<p data-start="1218" data-end="1255">If both similar<br data-start="1233" data-end="1236">
👉 Good model ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1257" data-end="1260">
<h1 data-section-id="kjbjg7" data-start="1262" data-end="1277">🎯 Final Rule</h1>
<p data-start="1279" data-end="1320">👉 <strong data-start="1282" data-end="1320">Always report: VALIDATION ACCURACY</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1322" data-end="1325">
<p data-start="1327" data-end="1489" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want next:<br>
✅ I can explain <strong data-start="1361" data-end="1396">overfitting in 2 lines for viva</strong><br data-start="1396" data-end="1399">
✅ Or help you <strong data-start="1413" data-end="1438">improve your accuracy</strong><br data-start="1438" data-end="1441">
✅ Or show how to <strong data-start="1458" data-end="1486">get 90%+ accuracy easily</strong> 🚀</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Share" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="More actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_o6_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" dir="auto" data-turn-id="ffa47264-5bfd-48a0-a6c9-f1de4d493e9c" data-testid="conversation-turn-69" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="ffa47264-5bfd-48a0-a6c9-f1de4d493e9c" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">what is epouch is higher than validation</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="293a399f-a2fa-4ab0-9003-b277aaeeaf0a" data-testid="conversation-turn-70" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="293a399f-a2fa-4ab0-9003-b277aaeeaf0a" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="42">Good — this is an <strong data-start="18" data-end="39">important concept</strong> 👍</p>
<hr data-start="44" data-end="47">
<h1 data-section-id="19nvpn6" data-start="49" data-end="109"><span role="text">✅ When <strong data-start="58" data-end="109">Training (Epoch) Accuracy &gt; Validation Accuracy</strong></span></h1>
<p data-start="111" data-end="139">👉 This situation is called:</p>
<h1 data-section-id="ycz98u" data-start="141" data-end="161"><span role="text">🔴 <strong data-start="146" data-end="161">Overfitting</strong></span></h1>
<hr data-start="163" data-end="166">
<h1 data-section-id="18d90tw" data-start="168" data-end="195">🧠 What It Means (Simple)</h1>
<p data-start="197" data-end="211">👉 Your model:</p>
<ul data-start="212" data-end="282">
<li data-section-id="10w58pl" data-start="212" data-end="247">
<p data-start="214" data-end="247">Learns training data <strong data-start="235" data-end="247">too well</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1b0z3j2" data-start="248" data-end="282">
<p data-start="250" data-end="282">But fails on <strong data-start="263" data-end="282">new/unseen data</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="284" data-end="287">
<h1 data-section-id="wknvcp" data-start="289" data-end="301">📊 Example</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="303" data-end="364"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Training Accuracy = 98%</span><br><span>Validation Accuracy = 82%</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="366" data-end="377">👉 Meaning:</p>
<ul data-start="378" data-end="441">
<li data-section-id="hwb2y9" data-start="378" data-end="413">
<p data-start="380" data-end="413">Model memorized training data ❌</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yuplhi" data-start="414" data-end="441">
<p data-start="416" data-end="441">Not generalizing well ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="443" data-end="446">
<h1 data-section-id="1jj3ofc" data-start="448" data-end="465">🎯 Real Meaning</h1>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="467" data-end="627" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="467" data-end="487"><tr data-start="467" data-end="487"><th data-start="467" data-end="476" data-col-size="sm" class="">Metric</th><th data-start="476" data-end="487" data-col-size="sm" class="">Meaning</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="506" data-end="627"><tr data-start="506" data-end="562"><td data-start="506" data-end="531" data-col-size="sm">High Training Accuracy</td><td data-start="531" data-end="562" data-col-size="sm">Model learned training data</td></tr><tr data-start="563" data-end="627"><td data-start="563" data-end="591" data-col-size="sm">Lower Validation Accuracy</td><td data-start="591" data-end="627" data-col-size="sm">Model performs worse on new data</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 33px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="629" data-end="653">👉 Gap = <strong data-start="638" data-end="653">overfitting</strong></p>
<hr data-start="655" data-end="658">
<h1 data-section-id="gd7xx4" data-start="660" data-end="681">⚠️ Why This Happens</h1>
<ul data-start="683" data-end="768">
<li data-section-id="11rtfm9" data-start="683" data-end="704">
<p data-start="685" data-end="704">Dataset too small</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ely0pf" data-start="705" data-end="726">
<p data-start="707" data-end="726">Model too complex</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="62vqrp" data-start="727" data-end="746">
<p data-start="729" data-end="746">Too many epochs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1731aot" data-start="747" data-end="768">
<p data-start="749" data-end="768">No regularization</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="770" data-end="773">
<h1 data-section-id="scgd25" data-start="775" data-end="793">🔧 How to Fix It</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="cfo73t" data-start="795" data-end="814">✅ 1. Add Dropout</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="815" data-end="841"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">Dropout</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0.5</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="843" data-end="846">
<h2 data-section-id="1naon6m" data-start="848" data-end="869">✅ 2. Reduce Epochs</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="870" data-end="913"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" 