<h1 data-section-id="1hi8pap" data-start="809" data-end="849">✅ If All These Work → Your Model is OK</h1>
<p data-start="851" data-end="918">✔ Loads without error<br data-start="872" data-end="875">
✔ Shows architecture<br data-start="895" data-end="898">
✔ Gives prediction</p>
<p data-start="920" data-end="957">👉 Then your model is <strong data-start="942" data-end="957">good to use</strong></p>
<hr data-start="959" data-end="962">
<h1 data-section-id="7sxl96" data-start="964" data-end="993">⚠️ RED FLAGS (Model NOT OK)</h1>
<p data-start="995" data-end="1006">If you see:</p>
<ul data-start="1008" data-end="1111">
<li data-section-id="k5n1dx" data-start="1008" data-end="1033">
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1033">❌ Error while loading</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rz5fnb" data-start="1034" data-end="1058">
<p data-start="1036" data-end="1058">❌ Output shape wrong</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11oh5h6" data-start="1059" data-end="1087">
<p data-start="1061" data-end="1087">❌ Always same prediction</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p160qd" data-start="1088" data-end="1111">
<p data-start="1090" data-end="1111">❌ Accuracy very low</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1113" data-end="1135">👉 Then problem exists</p>
<hr data-start="1137" data-end="1140">
<h1 data-section-id="s09wlb" data-start="1142" data-end="1163">🎯 BEST FINAL CHECK</h1>
<p data-start="1165" data-end="1181">👉 Ask yourself:</p>
<ul data-start="1183" data-end="1295">
<li data-section-id="18014ev" data-start="1183" data-end="1209">
<p data-start="1185" data-end="1209">Did training complete?</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xv8kw7" data-start="1210" data-end="1255">
<p data-start="1212" data-end="1255">Validation accuracy reasonable? (~80–90%)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xa7k3e" data-start="1256" data-end="1295">
<p data-start="1258" data-end="1295">Model predicts correctly on sample?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1318">👉 If YES → ✔ Perfect</p>
<hr data-start="1320" data-end="1323">
<h1 data-section-id="1q9t74" data-start="1325" data-end="1356">💡 Honest Insight (Important)</h1>
<p data-start="1358" data-end="1380">Even if model is “OK”:</p>
<ul data-start="1381" data-end="1451">
<li data-section-id="yd6qzt" data-start="1381" data-end="1412">
<p data-start="1383" data-end="1412">It’s <strong data-start="1388" data-end="1412">character-level only</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="48te3g" data-start="1413" data-end="1451">
<p data-start="1415" data-end="1451">Not perfect for real prescriptions</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1453" data-end="1469">👉 That’s normal</p>
<hr data-start="1471" data-end="1474">
<h1 data-section-id="1k29o6w" data-start="1476" data-end="1490">🎤 Viva Line</h1>
<p data-start="1492" data-end="1601">👉 <em data-start="1495" data-end="1601">“We validated the model by loading it, checking architecture, and testing predictions on sample inputs.”</em></p>
<hr data-start="1603" data-end="1606">
