<hr data-start="249" data-end="252">
<h1 data-section-id="1e7qwsd" data-start="254" data-end="305">✅ 🧠 GEMINI PROMPT (SEGMENTATION + FULL PIPELINE)</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="307" data-end="2937"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>You are an expert AI/ML and Computer Vision engineer.</span><br><br><span>I have a trained CNN model (model.h5) that recognizes handwritten characters (28x28 grayscale, similar to EMNIST dataset).</span><br><br><span>Build a complete end-to-end pipeline in Google Colab that takes a full prescription image and extracts readable text using the trained model.</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>1. LOAD MODEL</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Load model.h5 using TensorFlow/Keras</span><br><span>- Load class labels (characters)</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>2. INPUT IMAGE</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Load a prescription image (JPG/PNG)</span><br><span>- Resize image to 300x300</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>3. IMAGE PREPROCESSING</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Convert image to grayscale</span><br><span>- Apply:</span><br><span>    * Median blur</span><br><span>    * absdiff (difference with blurred image)</span><br><span>    * normalize</span><br><span>    * morphological opening</span><br><span>    * CLAHE (contrast enhancement)</span><br><span>- Apply thresholding to create binary image</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>4. CHARACTER SEGMENTATION</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Use OpenCV:</span><br><span>    * findContours()</span><br><span>    * detect individual characters</span><br><span>- For each contour:</span><br><span>    * get bounding box (x, y, w, h)</span><br><span>    * filter small noise (ignore very small boxes)</span><br><span>- Sort contours:</span><br><span>    * left to right</span><br><span>    * top to bottom (line-wise grouping)</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>5. CHARACTER EXTRACTION</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Crop each character from image</span><br><span>- Resize to 28x28</span><br><span>- Normalize pixel values</span><br><span>- Reshape to (1,28,28,1)</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>6. PREDICTION</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Pass each character to model</span><br><span>- Get predicted class using argmax</span><br><span>- Map index → actual character label</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>7. WORD FORMATION</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Combine characters into words based on spacing</span><br><span>- Combine words into lines</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>8. OUTPUT</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Print extracted text in readable format</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>9. VISUALIZATION (IMPORTANT)</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Draw bounding boxes on detected characters</span><br><span>- Show segmented characters</span><br><span>- Display final output text</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>10. IMPROVEMENTS</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>- Handle overlapping characters</span><br><span>- Improve contour filtering</span><br><span>- Adjust thresholding dynamically</span><br><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>GOAL:</span><br><span>-------------------------------</span><br><span>Input: Full prescription image</span><br><span>Output: Extracted readable text using CNN model</span><br><br><span>IMPORTANT:</span><br><span>- Do NOT predict on full image directly</span><br><span>- Always segment characters first</span><br><span>- Code must run fully in Google Colab</span><br><span>- Use clear comments</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
