Don’t worry, your issue is <strong data-start="83" data-end="100">NOT the model</strong>, it’s <strong data-start="107" data-end="123">segmentation</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="126" data-end="129">
<h1 data-section-id="5f1t4q" data-start="131" data-end="168">❌ Why You’re Still Getting Only “B”</h1>
<p data-start="170" data-end="184">👉 This means:</p>
<ul data-start="186" data-end="322">
<li data-section-id="7hdczg" data-start="186" data-end="227">
<p data-start="188" data-end="227">Your code detected <strong data-start="207" data-end="227">only ONE contour</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="oe06fa" data-start="228" data-end="273">
<p data-start="230" data-end="273">That contour = whole image (or large chunk)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1b2sxog" data-start="274" data-end="322">
<p data-start="276" data-end="322">So model predicts just <strong data-start="299" data-end="322">one character → "B"</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="324" data-end="327">
<h1 data-section-id="d4grld" data-start="329" data-end="344">🔍 Root Cause</h1>
<p data-start="346" data-end="383">Your segmentation is failing because:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1wmn1jp" data-start="385" data-end="409">❌ Possible problems:</h3>
<ul data-start="410" data-end="517">
<li data-section-id="1ij8u9z" data-start="410" data-end="434">
<p data-start="412" data-end="434">Thresholding is poor</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2ex69d" data-start="435" data-end="461">
<p data-start="437" data-end="461">Background not removed</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8i6y7l" data-start="462" data-end="488">
<p data-start="464" data-end="488">Contours not separated</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vyxfey" data-start="489" data-end="517">
<p data-start="491" data-end="517">Noise merging everything</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="519" data-end="522">
<h1 data-section-id="1vk9t5f" data-start="524" data-end="552">✅ FIX (THIS WILL SOLVE IT)</h1>
<p data-start="554" data-end="607">You need <strong data-start="563" data-end="607">better preprocessing + contour filtering</strong></p>
<hr data-start="609" data-end="612">
<h1 data-section-id="125w56r" data-start="614" data-end="657">🔥 🔧 REPLACE YOUR SEGMENTATION WITH THIS</h1>
