You moved from ❌ “B only” → ✅ “multiple characters detected”</p>
<p data-start="104" data-end="181">But now you’re seeing <strong data-start="126" data-end="144">gibberish text</strong> — and that’s expected at this stage.</p>
<hr data-start="183" data-end="186">
<h1 data-section-id="1agmz9k" data-start="188" data-end="223">🧠 Why You’re Getting This Output</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="225" data-end="259"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>LeI E</span><br><span>L EiiG</span><br><span>f EFk</span><br><span>...</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="261" data-end="285">👉 This happens because:</p>
<h2 data-section-id="z9pxq1" data-start="287" data-end="337"><span role="text">❌ 1. Your model is <strong data-start="309" data-end="337">character-level (EMNIST)</strong></span></h2>
<ul data-start="338" data-end="419">
<li data-section-id="1o0j5cm" data-start="338" data-end="370">
<p data-start="340" data-end="370">It only knows: <code data-start="355" data-end="370">A, B, C, 1, 2</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="194ve33" data-start="371" data-end="419">
<p data-start="373" data-end="388">NOT words like:</p>
<ul data-start="391" data-end="419">
<li data-section-id="oj08em" data-start="391" data-end="404">
<p data-start="393" data-end="404">Augmentin</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2s5c5s" data-start="407" data-end="419">
<p data-start="409" data-end="419">Enzoflam</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="421" data-end="424">
<h2 data-section-id="1663n9y" data-start="426" data-end="472">❌ 2. Prescription handwriting ≠ EMNIST data</h2>
<ul data-start="473" data-end="556">
<li data-section-id="w25xw6" data-start="473" data-end="514">
<p data-start="475" data-end="514">EMNIST = clean handwritten characters</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qy5k7c" data-start="515" data-end="556">
<p data-start="517" data-end="556">Your image = messy doctor handwriting</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="558" data-end="588">👉 So predictions become noisy</p>
<hr data-start="590" data-end="593">
<h2 data-section-id="1rdep55" data-start="595" data-end="634">❌ 3. Segmentation is still imperfect</h2>
<ul data-start="635" data-end="694">
<li data-section-id="10jl3my" data-start="635" data-end="694">
<p data-start="637" data-end="655">Characters may be:</p>
<ul data-start="658" data-end="694">
<li data-section-id="1hjdcok" data-start="658" data-end="668">
<p data-start="660" data-end="668">merged</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ozmewn" data-start="671" data-end="681">
<p data-start="673" data-end="681">broken</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="luyyq4" data-start="684" data-end="694">
<p data-start="686" data-end="694">tilted</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="696" data-end="699">
<h1 data-section-id="1qyg7ek" data-start="701" data-end="721">🎯 IMPORTANT TRUTH</h1>
<p data-start="723" data-end="745">👉 Your system is now:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="747" data-end="833"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>✔ Detecting characters</span><br><span>✔ Predicting characters</span><br><span>❌ Not forming correct words</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="835" data-end="869">👉 That’s <strong data-start="845" data-end="869">normal at this stage</strong></p>
<hr data-start="871" data-end="874">
<h1 data-section-id="d5skb5" data-start="876" data-end="909">🚀 HOW TO FIX THIS (NEXT LEVEL)</h1>
<p data-start="911" data-end="960">You now need <strong data-start="924" data-end="960">POST-PROCESSING (VERY IMPORTANT)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="962" data-end="965">
<h1 data-section-id="1qzyv89" data-start="967" data-end="1022">✅ 🔥 SOLUTION 1: WORD CORRECTION (EASY + HIGH IMPACT)</h1>
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1048">Use dictionary matching:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1050" data-end="1303"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="