start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-turn-start-message="true" tabindex="0"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="118">Got it 👍 — here’s a <strong data-start="21" data-end="80">clean prompt you can directly paste into Gemini (Colab)</strong> when it asks for medicine dictionary.</p>
<hr data-start="120" data-end="123">
<h1 data-section-id="scky5h" data-start="125" data-end="167">✅ 🧠 GEMINI PROMPT (MEDICINE DICTIONARY)</h1>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="169" data-end="933"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Use the following medicine dictionary for correcting OCR output:</span><br><br><span>medicines = [</span><br><span>    "augmentin",</span><br><span>    "enzoflam",</span><br><span>    "pantoprazole",</span><br><span>    "pandom",</span><br><span>    "hexigel",</span><br><span>    "paracetamol",</span><br><span>    "amoxicillin",</span><br><span>    "ibuprofen",</span><br><span>    "crocin",</span><br><span>    "dolo",</span><br><span>    "azithromycin",</span><br><span>    "cetirizine",</span><br><span>    "metformin",</span><br><span>    "omeprazole",</span><br><span>    "ranitidine",</span><br><span>    "diclofenac"</span><br><span>]</span><br><br><span>Apply fuzzy matching using difflib.get_close_matches().</span><br><br><span>Rules:</span><br><span>- Convert all predicted words to lowercase before matching</span><br><span>- Match each word with the closest medicine name</span><br><span>- Only replace if similarity &gt; 0.6</span><br><span>- If no match found, keep original word</span><br><span>- Ensure final output contains readable medicine names</span><br><br><span>Goal:</span><br><span>Convert noisy OCR predictions into correct medicine names.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="935" data-end="938">
<h1 data-section-id="1mix4j0" data-start="940" data-end="962">🎯 What This Will Do</h1>
<p data-start="964" data-end="976">👉 Converts:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="977" data-end="1055"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>paracitamol → paracetamol  </span><br><span>crocim → crocin  </span><br><span>enzoflm → enzoflam  </span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
